Analysis, Assessment, & Fleet Feedback

The Navy Assessment Program: Funds the analytical studies that provide data-driven insights into fleet performance, readiness, and capability gaps, directly informing the entire
force.

The Navy Readiness Reporting Enterprise (NRRE): Sustains the systems used by all fleet commands to report, track, and analyze readiness data, providing an authoritative picture
of our warfighting health.

Quantitative Fleet Feedback (QFF) Program: Supports the collection of objective performance data from all major fleet exercises and training events, providing the raw data
needed for rigorous tactical analysis by the Warfare Development Centers.




